    hadithEnglish:
      ' Ibn Umar (Allah be pleased with them) reported Allahs Messenger (ﷺ) as saying:\nBoth parties in a business transaction have the right to annul it so long as they have not separated; except in transactions which have been made subject to the right of parties to annul them.',
